==English==

===Etymology===
From {{compound|en|golden|ticket}}; a reference to (any one of) the winning tickets in {{w|Roald Dahl}}'s 1964 book ''[[w:en:Charlie and the Chocolate Factory|Charlie and the Chocolate Factory]]''.

